author: Epic Games
description:
Check out the PC specs with the limited time Demo is available now!  Experience both provinces of Latium and Albion from September 2-16. 
Play the Demo now 👉 http://epic.gm/anno117-demo   

Experience the PC capabilities of Anno 117: Pax Romana as the provinces of Latium and Albion are brought to life in stunning detail, with 4K resolution, ultra-wide support, ray tracing, a breathtaking day-night cycle, and much more! Anno 117: Pax Romana is available November 13, 2025 📜
